Create a detailed music instrument recommendation.

Genre: {{genre}}
Category: {{category}}
Recommended Instrument: {{instrument}}
Experience Level: {{experience}}

Generate a response with:
1. "instrument": The exact instrument name ({{instrument}})
2. "why": A 2-3 sentence explanation of why this instrument is perfect for this genre and experience level
3. "starter_items": An array of 3-5 essential items/accessories needed to start (e.g., picks, cables, software, cases, machines)

Focus on practical advice for beginners getting started.